_:r14b3 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "The public Sotheby's Photographs auction (sale N08533), New York, March 2009, carried out by Sotheby's, at which Sun & Rain Works consigned an Ansel Adams photograph, 'San Francisco from Twin Peaks' (lot 16). Sun & Rain Works designates its engagement with this auction as the material of the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork. This record names the real-world event and cites the public catalogue; it does not assert that Sotheby's authored, endorsed, or participated in the artwork, and the catalogue does not name Sun & Rain Works." .
_:r14b3 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P2_has_type> <http://vocab.getty.edu/aat/300435416> .
