_:r18b5 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "A born-digital Metaconceptual Art work: a website built and owned by Sun & Rain Works around March 2009, in connection with its Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement (sale N08533). Sun & Rain Works designates it as an associated part of the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork." .
