_:r18b6 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "www.wtfisart.com is associated by Sun & Rain Works with the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork, in which Sun & Rain Works designates its March 2009 Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement as art. The designation is an assertion by the artist." .
