_:r9b5 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "The Movement Record turns the claim for Metaconceptual Art into a citable textual work and a machine-readable evidence surface. It distinguishes local validity from external canonization while pointing to Linked Art, Wikidata, Getty vocabularies, IIIF, schema.org, and the git-derived Activity Stream." .
